                            <Paragraph>
                              <TextRuns>
                                <TextRun>
                                  <Value>HEREBY CONFIRM MY AGREEMENT AND UNDERTAKINGS TO THE DEVELOPER AND THE SUB-DEVELOPER ON THE MATTERS BELOW RELATED TO THE MANAGEMENT AND OPERATION OF THE COMMON ARE OF THE PROJECT AND THE COMMUNITY HOUSE AS FOLLOWS:</Value>
