                          <Paragraphs>
                            <Paragraph>
                              <TextRuns>
                                <TextRun>
                                  <Value>The Buyer agrees and accepts the Developer to be the organization implementing the construction of common infrastructure, ensuring the traffic connection, placing the water supply and drainage waiting stub-outs, the power source stub-outs, the water source stub-outs to serve the Component Project Residents (including the Buyer).</Value>
