                                    <Color>#000000</Color>
                                  </Style>
                                </TextRun>
                                <TextRun>
                                  <Value>") to perform the management, operation, maintenance and repair of the Common Area of the Project on a fee basis by collecting fees and maintenance funds from the Sub-developer and the Component Project Residents (including the Buyer).</Value>
