                          <KeepTogether>true</KeepTogether>
                          <Paragraphs>
                            <Paragraph>
                              <TextRuns>
                                <TextRun>
                                  <Value>The Buyer agrees and undertakes to comply with the Internal Regulations of the Housing Area in the Project, fully and timely complete the obligation to pay the management fee for the Common Area of the Project, utility usage fee and maintenance fund contribution as notified by the Developer/Management Company and Sub-developer and to cooperate and be directly responsible to the Developer or the Management Company for the Buyer’s use of the Common Area of the Project and the Community House.</Value>
