                            <Paragraph>
                              <TextRuns>
                                <TextRun>
                                  <Value>The Buyer agrees and undertakes to comply with the internal regulations for the management and use of the Common Area of the Component Project, which may be a separate document or part of the Internal Regulations of the Housing Area.</Value>
