                    <TablixCell>
                      <CellContents>
                        <Textbox Name="Textbox89">
                          <CanGrow>true</CanGrow>
                          <KeepTogether>true</KeepTogether>
                          <Paragraphs>
                            <Paragraph>
                              <TextRuns>
                                <TextRun>
                                  <Value>The Buyer agrees and undertakes to pay the management fee for the Common Area of the Project for a period of 01 (one) year from the date on which the Sub-developer hands over the first house to its Customer in the Component Project and to pay the contribution of maintenance funds through the Sub-developer in accordance with the Sale and Purchase Agreement, for the Sub-developer to transfer such fees and funds to the Developer and/or the Management Company. From the second year onwards, the management fee for the Common Area of the Project and the newly incurred maintenance cost (if any) shall be paid by the Buyer according to the notice of the Developer and/or the Management Company.</Value>
                                  <Style>
                                    <FontStyle>Normal</FontStyle>
                                    <FontFamily>Times New Roman</FontFamily>
                                    <FontSize>12pt</FontSize>
                                    <FontWeight>Normal</FontWeight>
                                    <TextDecoration>None</TextDecoration>
                                  </Style>
                                </TextRun>
                              </TextRuns>
                              <Style />
