                              <TextRuns>
                                <TextRun>
                                  <Value>The land area used as the basis for calculating the management fee for the Common Area of the Project is determined according to the Land Use Right Certificate issued to the Sub-developer or the Buyer from time to time (or the based on the sale and purchase agreement signed between the Sub-developer and the Buyer in case the Buyer has not been granted a Land Use Right Certificate).</Value>
