                          <Paragraphs>
                            <Paragraph>
                              <TextRuns>
                                <TextRun>
                                  <Value>The works, areas, utilities, and equipment in the Common Area of the Project may be re-determined and adjusted by the Developer to suit the current management and operation status of the Project according to the written notice of the Developer or the principle and/or actual, operative documents/drawings issued by the Developer.</Value>
