                            <Paragraph>
                              <TextRuns>
                                <TextRun>
                                  <Value>The Buyer agrees that the Developer may, at its own discretion, carry out the procedures for handing over the Project's infrastructure system to the State agency or a third party and receive reimbursement for investment costs (if any), and the Developer/Management Company may, at their own discretion, manage and use such reimbursement.</Value>
